summary: This is a Bank of America personal signature card and substitute Form W-9 for a checking account titled 'Temporary Signature Card'. It documents the account setup, terms, and taxpayer identification certification, with a date of August 7, 2012, and appears to be a standard banking form.

events.title: Bank Account Setup
events.description: A Bank of America personal checking account titled 'Temporary Signature Card' was established, involving the completion of a signature card and Form W-9.

keyFacts: Document is a Bank of America personal signature card and substitute Form W-9 for a checking account.
Account is titled 'Temporary Signature Card' and is a MYACCESS CHECKING account.
The form includes certification of taxpayer identification number under penalties of perjury.
Document is dated August 7, 2012, from the Pelham Parkway banking center.
No named individuals are listed in the provided text; it appears to be a template or partially redacted form.
